OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779196276
OL,3,CDemonstration against scrapping of
OL,4,Cjury trials takes place
OL,6,FA demonstration has taken place in
OL,7,FCarlisle in opposition of proposed
OL,8,Fchanges to the justice system.
OL,10,FThe Government is working on proposals
OL,11,Ffor criminal cases with a likely
OL,12,Fsentence of three years or less to be
OL,13,Fheard by a single judge at Crown
OL,14,FCourts, rather than by a jury.
OL,16,FThe protest was part of a nationwide
OL,17,Fcampaign from The Jury Alliance, with
OL,18,Fa presence expected at over 30 courts.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
