PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779196276
OL,3,CDemonstration against scrapping of
OL,4,Cjury trials takes place
OL,6,FIn response, a Ministry of Justice
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The Crown Court is
OL,8,Fon the brink of collapse, with over
OL,9,F80,000 cases as of December, and
OL,10,Fvictims face devastating delays
OL,11,Fresulting from years of neglect.
OL,13,F"Over 90% of criminal cases are
OL,14,Falready dealt with in magistrates'
OL,15,Fcourts ` fairly ` without juries. It
OL,16,Fis only by pulling every lever at our
OL,17,Fdisposal - pragmatic structural
OL,18,Freform, record financial investment
OL,19,Fand modernisation - that we can drive
OL,20,Fdown the backlog."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
