FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779196276
OL,3,CDemonstration against scrapping of
OL,4,Cjury trials takes place
OL,6,FDefendants in the US can waive their
OL,7,Fright to a jury trial, while in
OL,8,Fcountries like France and Japan, they
OL,9,Fare reserved only for the most serious
OL,10,Fof cases where judges sit beside
OL,11,Fjurors.
OL,13,FMany European countries, such as
OL,14,FFrance, Sweden, Denmark and others,
OL,15,Fhave scrapped the traditional jury
OL,16,Fsystem and most trials are decided by
OL,17,Fprofessional judges or mixed tribunals.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
